law.history: Repealed 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 428, sec. 4, effective July 15, 1982; amended 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 428, sec. 4. -- Created 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 232, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Use and administration of jail in county containing city of first class, after establishment of workhouse or penal farm.
metadata.lrc-note: . This section was amended by 1982 Acts Chapter 385, Section 43 and repealed by 1982 Acts Chapter 428, Section 4. Pursuant to KRS 446.260, the repeal prevails.
